          "COMMENT": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "-By authors. The profiling technique to large number of",
                "samples was applied. There were implanted with Ti-48",
                "ions at 50-KeV ion implanter whose mass resolution",
                "allowed the separation of the Ti isotopes. A uniformly",
                "area of 6 mm diameter was obtained by sweeping the ion",
                "beam electrostatically over the sample. Polycrystalline",
                "foils of Fe and Ni with a purity of 99.99% were used as",
                "host materials."
              ]
            }
          ],
